        <a href="/blog/online-base64-to-file/" class="block rounded-lg border border-hairline bg-canvas p-4 no-underline hover:shadow-level-3 transition-all"><p class="text-[14px] font-medium leading-5 text-ink">Base64 to Downloadable File</p><p class="text-[12px] leading-4 text-mute mt-1">Generic file conversion for any format</p></a>
        <a href="/blog/svg-to-base64/" class="block rounded-lg border border-hairline bg-canvas p-4 no-underline hover:shadow-level-3 transition-all"><p class="text-[14px] font-medium leading-5 text-ink">SVG to Base64 Guide</p><p class="text-[12px] leading-4 text-mute mt-1">Vector graphics encoding for CSS and HTML</p></a>
